show.title: Revenge of XXL Husband
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/sYdkvk
show.description: Since she no longer likes her fat husband, the wife finds a new partner and divorces him. The husband, humiliated and ashamed, and for revenge, loses weight and comes back. Unable to recognize the handsome husband, the ex-wife falls in love with him again. But by then, the ex-husband has found his life partner, who was by his side during that difficult time. And with her, the ex-husband takes revenge on his ex-wife.
